ighter fare options there’s something delicious for everyone at olive garden discover more wwwolivegardencom find an olive garden near you job opportunities at olive garden contact olive garden olive garden gift cards join the olive garden eclub olive garden is community every day in every olive garden location across the country team members spend extra time to prepare package freeze and store unserved surplus food for donation to local food banks shelters and other charitable organizations  last year those restaurants donated three million pounds of wholesome and readytoeat food  since  olive garden has donated  million pounds of food to help those in need donated pounds of food  million learn more the darden foundation gives  million to feeding america july   longhorn steakhouse olive garden seasons  the capital grille yard house olive garden bartender is friend to everyone july   olive garden careers people view more darden digest explore our other brands olive garden longhorn steakhouse cheddars yardhouse capital grille seasons  bahama breeze eddie vs media contact twitter youtube linkedin copyright  darden concepts inc all rights reserved legal notices  privacy notice  your california privacy rights darden flashratings  contact us facebook autocomplete demo post a rating  month price target   trending sign up log in contact flashratings your emotional state excited confused worried upset panicked angry creative commons — attributionsharealike  unported — cc bysa  skip to content menu help us build a vibrant collaborative global commons donate now creative commons creative commons license deed attributionsharealike  unported cc bysa  this is a humanreadable summary of and not a substitute for the license disclaimer you are free to share — copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format adapt — remix transform and build upon the material for any purpose even commercially the licensor cannot revoke these freedoms as long as you follow the license terms